  "title": "✨ Junior Marketing & Promotions Executive (Training Provided) ✨",
  "description": "<h3>Junior Marketing & Promotions Executive (Training Provided)</h3><p>New to working life? No worries — everyone starts somewhere. This role is perfect if you want to <strong>learn real marketing skills</strong>, meet people, and gain hands-on experience while getting proper guidance and support.</p><p></p><p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p><p>📌 Support <strong>marketing and promotional activities</strong></p><p>💬 Engage customers during <strong>brand promotions</strong></p><p>📊 Learn <strong>communication, presentation, and sales fundamentals</strong></p><p>🤝 Assist the team during campaign execution</p><p>📈 Develop confidence and workplace skills</p><p></p><p><strong>What You’ll Get</strong></p><p>🎓 Structured <strong>training from the basics</strong></p><p>👔 Guidance from experienced mentors</p><p>🏢 Exposure to <strong>real brand campaigns</strong></p><p>✈️ Travel opportunities and <strong>performance-based earnings</strong></p><p>🚀 Clear progression opportunities</p><p></p><p><strong>This Role Is For You If</strong></p><p>🧩 You’re starting your <strong>first full-time role</strong></p><p>👍 You have a positive, learning-focused attitude<br /><br />👥 You enjoy working in a team environment</p><p>✅ <strong>No experience required </strong>— training is provided</p><p></p>",
